@node Oprogramu "Introduction"
Do You want to search some files or keywords in the Aminet Index?
Do You want to do it fast?
and do You have the Aminet Index (no problem to Get it, If you have
 Internet) ?

    then

AmIndex is For You.

AmIndex is small helper For searching through the Aminet Index. You only enter
the Word (or a part of Word) and then click to search. Very simply, isn't?

After a few seconds You have the results.



For development AmIndex is used PCQPascal1.2d (thanks Patrick Quaid) and GUI is
in 70% (+-) in GadToolsBox2.0b (thanks Jan van den Baard)

@endnode

@node Shareware
This program is @{FG SHINE}shareware@{FG TEXT}. If You like @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} You should be a registered user.
The registration fee is 10 @{FG SHINE}USD/DM@{FG TEXT} or equivalent in other currency.
Please, send only banknotes and NO COINS!

If You Are a registered user of Uzemi (by Blue Legend) then the registration fee
is 5 @{FG SHINE}USD/DM@{FG TEXT}.

If You want to register, please print and fillout the Registation form and send
Registration form + one disk + Registration fee to address of @{"author" link kontakt}

You will Get the disk back with the latest version of @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} and a @{FG SHINE}keyfile@{FG Text}.

After registration you have an update (versions 1.xx) for free.
For upgrading to version 2.xx your registration fee will be lower.

