@node Pozadavky "Requirements"
@{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} needs

 - min. OS 3.0

 - reqtools.library version 38 or greater (included)

 - Aminet index :-)

 - about 150 kB if free memory

 - harddisk (very, very recommended :-)


Recommended:

 - AmIndex.keyfile :-)

 - Installer for instalation

 - AmIndex.catalog (localization)

 - medplayer.library version 2 or greater (for music)

@endnode

@node Instalace "Instalation"

Please, use the installation utility. :)
@endnode

@node Program
Usage of @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} should be intuitive, but If you have some problems here is
a brief discription


 @{FG SHINE}Main window@{FG TEXT}

 New Index     -  Complex analyze of Aminet-index. Is need for the work of @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu}

 Search        -  @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} looks for the file which is entered in
                  gadget FIND

 Close Results -  Close all windows with results of searching. You can open
                  max 10 windows. Each of it can have max 1024 records

 Find          -  Here you should enter then text for searching


In right part of main window is the list of all directories where you can search.
Click on some directory mean, that the searching will be processed only in
selected directory.


 @{FG SHINE}Menu@{FG TEXT}

 New Index    -  the same as in main window

 Reset        -  Set @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} to initial state. It deletes all informations about
                 current Aminet-index, so be carefully.

 Preferences  -  Call a preferences window

 About        -  no comment :-)

 Quit         -  Oh, don't select this item so often :-)
@endnode

@node Preference "Preferences"
Here you can find a description of preferences.

 Requesters:

 All        -  @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} show all its requesters

 Important  -  ... and now only important

 None       -  no requesters will be shown


 Case Sensitive  -  If this gadget isn't checked then the searching is case
                    insensitive (that mean lowercase is equal to uppercase
                    of chars)

 Exclude Mods    -  If this Gadget is checked then @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} ignore directory "mods".
                    It speed up the searching.

 Only First      -  Program finds only one (and first) record

 Files           -  If this gadget is checked @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} search after beginning
                    of the files, in other case is enable fulltext search.


 Save, Use, Cancel
            -  the same like in other preferences

@endnode

@node Tooltypes
And here are @{FG SHINE}Tooltypes@{FG TEXT}:

 KEYFILE   - If you are a registered user and you wish to have a @{"keyfile" link shareware}
             in other directory than @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} search, enter here a path
             to your keyfile

             @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu} tryes these directories to search keyfile
                - current directory (the place of AmIndex)
                - directory keyfile/
                - directory DEVS:
                - directory DEVS:keyfiles/
                - directory L:
                - directory ENVARC:
                - directory ENV:

 TASKPRI   - Set the Taskpriority of @{"AmIndex" link Oprogramu}

 MUSIC     - MUSIC=ON  switch on the music
             MUSIC=OFF music will not be loaded :-|

             If you Set the tooltype MUSIC=ON then you can
             switch on/off music by hitting 'm'

@endnode

